# GraphOne Frontend Engineering Trial

A pixel-perfect frontend implementation of the **GraphOne AI Intelligence Platform** built as part of the **Frontend Engineer Trial Assignment**.

The project focuses on recreating the provided UI references using a modern React-based stack while maintaining clean architecture, reusable components, and responsive design.

---

