# ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/YOUR_REPOSITORY.git
```

Move into the project

```bash
cd YOUR_REPOSITORY
```

Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

Run locally

```bash
npm run dev
```

Visit

```text
http://localhost:3000
```

